div.p:
Answ. This is a false Doctrine, for God gives Grace to all; The Grace of God which brings Salvation, hath appeared unto all men,
 as it is written, which Grace teacheth the Saints to deny all ungodliness;
 and the wicked turn the grace of God into wantonness: but the true knowledge of God is given but to a few; and not many Wise men after the flesh are called, but God chooseth the Poor and Contemptible (as saith Paul) to confound the Wise and Mighty of this World; and yet God gives Knowledge to Rich and Poor without respect of persons, as it pleaseth Him.
